          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/47817b4476bcd8b44c86c87debf042f2_6337439283994279801.png",
                "id": "talent92779",
                "key": "Rippling Slash",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Rippling Slash"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Deals 2 <span style=\"color: #80C0FF\">Hydro DMG</span>, then performs \"<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Prepare Skill</span>\" for <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Rippling Blades</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Rippling Blades</span></strong><br><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span><br>Deals 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/09d978772c4b7b95a9b3896de9e32f9a_5358503475823437692.png",
                "id": "talent83499",
                "key": "Vortex Edge",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Vortex Edge"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Deals 3 <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>. Creates 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Curse of the Undercurrent</span> on the opponent's side of the field.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Curse of the Undercurrent</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Combat Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When character(s) on this side of the playing field use Elemental Skills or Elemental Bursts:</span> They must spend 1 extra Elemental Die.<br><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Usage(s): 2</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/d93cfa2833ead49715475616489de21c_4457973577827511118.png",
                "id": "talent26532",
                "key": "Torrential Shock",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "hydro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Torrential Shock"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>(Passive) When the battle begins, this character gains <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Watery Rebirth</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Watery Rebirth</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Status</span><br><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">When the character to which this is attached would be defeated:</span> Remove this effect, ensure the character <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">will not be defeated</span>, and heal them to 4 HP. After this effect is triggered, <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Physical DMG</span> this character deals is converted to <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span>, and <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro DMG</span> +1.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/1bbe84955410406904930648b9a4dd36_4745773643325552738.png",
                "id": "talent67413",
                "key": "Watery Rebirth ",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Watery Rebirth "
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Applies Hydro and can trigger the following Elemental Reactions:</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Vaporize</span>: DMG +2 for this instance</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, deal 1 Piercing DMG to all opposing characters except the target</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Frozen</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, the target is unable to perform any Actions this Round (Can be removed in advance after the target receives +2 Physical or Pyro DMG)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\"> + </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">] Bloom</span>: DMG +1 for this instance, creates a [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Dendro Core</span>] that grants +2 DMG to the next instance of Pyro or Electro DMG</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/a126c6a302d81c07e19cf9a9f1260f90_346957950846458589.png",
                "id": "talent87588",
                "key": "Hydro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Hydro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Physical DMG</span></strong><br>Physical DMG will not apply any Elements, nor can it engage in Elemental Reactions.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Prepare Skill</span></strong></p><p>Some Skills cannot be used directly. Instead, they need to be <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span> over a certain number of turns.<br>When it is a certain player's turn, and this player's active character is currently <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill, this player's turn will be skipped. If the Skill has finished being <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepared</span>, the character will directly use that Skill at this time. (Skills that require <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> cannot activate effects triggered by \"using a Skill\" or \"triggering an Elemental Reaction\" or other such effects.)<br>Only active characters can <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">prepare</span> Skills, and if an active character who is <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparing</span> a Skill gets switched off-field, their <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">preparation</span> will be interrupted.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Usage(s)</span></strong><br>After this card's effect is triggered, 1 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usage</span> of it will be consumed.<br>This card will be discarded immediately once it has 0 <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Usages</span> remaining.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Immunity to Defeat</span></strong><br>Certain effects will grant characters an <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">immunity to being defeated</span> when their HP hits 0, and will heal them for a certain amount thereafter.<br>When this occurs, characters will not be regarded as having experienced a <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">defeat.</span> (Hence, their attached equipment and statuses will not be removed, and their Energy will remain uncleared.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/04/23/35428890/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_5289754977550999399.png",
                "id": "talent36445",
                "key": "Detailed Rules",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Detailed Rules"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
