                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(255, 255, 255)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Tavern Challenge: Serious Showdown - Abyss Herald's Tides",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "level": 2,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:rgb(255, 215, 128)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Stage Introduction",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "\"Meow.\" \"In time, cat mothers would tell tales of that shadow to unruly kittens, and these tales would always being with the sound of lapping tides...\"",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
